{"url": "https://ew.com/tv/2018/05/04/american-idol-renewed-abc/", "text": "The results are in\u2026 and American Idol will return for a second season on ABC.\n\nOn Friday, the network announced a renewal for the singing competition series, while also revealing that judges Katy Perry, Luke Bryan, and Lionel Richie, as well as host Ryan Seacrest, will be all be back.\n\n\u201cY\u2019ALL! I\u2019m having TWO much fun to stop now\u2026 so why don\u2019t we keep it going!?\u201d tweeted Perry. \u201cEXCITED TO ANNOUNCE that @lukebryanofficial, @lionelrichie, @ryanseacrest and yours truly will be BACK with another season of #AmericanIdol on @ABCnetwork.\u201d\n\nBryan, Richie, and Seacrest also shared their excitement on social media.\n\nAfter 15 seasons on Fox, American Idol returned in March on a new network with a new set of judges. The current season will crown the latest winner on May 21.", "images": ["https://ew.com/thmb/x1yJDOmuvXrlYl8sZrkso_vYnHc=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/survivor-49-Rizo-Velovic-jeff-probst-111825-6285824536f945cb81e5876c09406764.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/-ivDnUSajL4K0kJbIidzxPPC14U=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/ariana-grande-AMERICAN-HORROR-STORY-HOTEL-Evan-Peters-AMERICAN-HORROR-STORY-Sarah-Paulson-110525-03f4062fe1cf4ba2b0069fca7f0f0363.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/B8x_obICG-AoqJvKQitEIRLAXlY=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/jimmy-kimmel-361-110725-74833fe28df846d3bee99a83b0b38cbc.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/SghPzU-KKwcLq-2EmQLmzJa2310=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Tom-Bergeron-Bobby-Bones-111325-e73e5ebcfff749c9b6228b8c9f489670.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/CZnm21SNYBYdPch0gJHc6Cs3pk0=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Randy-Madden-110425-63e0484e2a8545c69986482763639f1b.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/eTFr4-lkF0i4aLAhT0cX_bGVsq8=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Maksim-Chmerkovskiy